Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokozuna! I need lumber! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, those two are extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from Tom's Workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're barely keeping up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It boggles the mind that they\Ncould work at such a crazy pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And there isn't even the\Nslightest fault in their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna get anywhere by\Njust sitting here and admiring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show them what us\NDock #1 workers are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokozuna! Guys! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered you used to collect junk
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and built a bunch of weird\Nbattleships on this scrap heap island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't like me building weapons, did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. On top of that, they were\Nused to frame Tom-san as a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But by looking at this, I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...that your experience building those\Nbattleships wasn't a waste at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Is that sarcasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show Tom-san that\Nthe Moron-ky from back then has...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With this ship, going to the New\NWorld is no longer a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even before Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can resolutely stand proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Iceberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought those two would\Nwork together to build a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...! What the hell are you doing\Ninstead of helping me with work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you keep making\Nunstable stuff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It's none of\Nyour business, Stupid-berg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what's with him?!\NYou should just kick out an idiot like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't say that. He's a fellow ship builder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,His shipbuilding skills are already almost\Non par with the craftsmen on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...though what he makes is shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just always honest, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You two will definitely become\Nworld-class shipbuilding engineers someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things are going,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks like we'll be able to\Nfinish it sooner than we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Iceberg, let me tell you one thing.\NThis isn't just another pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. You've put your heart into--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats went head-on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,against not only Navy Headquarters,\Nbut the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ship they'll be traveling on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, the mayor of Water Seven,\Ntook part in building it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If that becomes known, you could be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You do understand that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, did you forget what Tom-san said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky, there's no such thing\Nas blueprints for a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If the sailors who board a ship put up\Na skull flag, then it's a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If they put up a seagull flag,\Nthen it's a Navy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you wanna build,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but a man should be resolutely\Nproud of the ship he built!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Galley-La has been building ships\Nbased on that creed all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm giving you a hand\Ntowards achieving your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I feel that... I'm not in my right mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I asked you to\Ngive me a hand, Stupid-berg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You abandoned your real name
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and your body, too, is like that\Nof a completely different man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you haven't changed at all.\NYou're just the way you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream... Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Tom-san back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Sea train!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna build ships anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't love ships that hurt\Nthe people I really care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're my goal after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want you to come back\Nand teach me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...build a dream ship someday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship that resolutely and proudly traverses
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,even uncharted waves at edges of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream ship like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This bites... My body... is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if I'll die like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see no one on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An abandoned ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Scrap wood... Scrap iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This place makes me... feel quite at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something\Nabout my disabled body first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... anyway, what's up with\Nthat funny looking body of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Since my whole\Nbody became of no use,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I rebuilt my body using iron\Nscraps and escaped death!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We never change, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever we meet face to face,\Nwe yell at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I still won't forgive you... and you\Nmay feel the same about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky... I'm... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...glad that... you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell with "I'm glad that you're alive"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I'm alive, he ended up\Nhelping me achieve my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite an idiot, too, Iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whoa, Luffy! What a coincidence\Nto see you in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just taking a stroll...\Nbut, well, this must just be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do? I'll come\Nback and rejoin the gang!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is pattern 53.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But not being able to use it\Nunless they find me is a flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I should take\Nsome initiative myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! That's what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why're they all looking so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems like the crew's gotten\Nreally disorganized and on-edge without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then, for everyone's sake, I'll just—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern 34!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ah-choo! Ah-choo!\NGeez, that night breeze is cold!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sneeze loudly so that they'd hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the crucial moment. I definitely\Nhave to act like this is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, is that you over there, Usopp?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well, I just happened to be passing by."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"You shouldn't stay outside, you'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside and have something warm."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, yeah? Well, I know\Nexactly how you guys feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you need me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's let bygones be bygones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're going to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The new ship is coming\Ntogether quickly, and I haven't yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to somehow rejoin the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:13:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now that it's come to this,\NI'll come up with more patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro! I brought some food and drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For you Galley-La guys, too! Take a little break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought you cold cola, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We chilled them good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaay! I was pretty hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you brought some\Nof this stuff, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Iceberg-san! Franky!\NGo ahead and take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys have been working\Nwithout eating or drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can keep on going like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we can take a break later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... then I'll take you up on that offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not a bad idea for me\Nto replenish cola and power up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Replenishment completed! Super... Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah, he is!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky, what're you going to do\Nonce the ship is completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you hand the ship over to the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to be satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you've achieved your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You like those guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I told you so many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention whatsoever\Nof leaving this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm gonna go back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokozuna, you sit back and relax for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Paulie, it's you guys' turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're so exhausted that we\Ncan't even manage a late-night snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are the very\Ndefinition of inexhaustible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a party once the ship is completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a short time, but I had fun with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally met someone worthy\Nof entrusting with my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As I promised, I'm gonna build an amazing ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Iceberg! Why don't you take it\Neasy and get some sleep, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm feeling super energetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you watching this, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You were called a legendary shipwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like your skills and spirit were\Npassed down to your disciples splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A log has been stored!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Log Pose is pointing to the next island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, all we need now is the ship!\NI'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He told us not to come until it's\Ndone because he wants to surprise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know where\Nfollowing that log will take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It somehow looks like it's\Npointing a little downwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is. The next island\Nis a paradise on the seabed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! F-F-Fishman Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What's wrong, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island, huh?\NI'm not sure how to feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it reminds me\Nof what happened in your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But, well, they weren't just Fishmen,\Nbut pirates too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! You really hit the nail on the head, shithead!\NImpressive for a {\i1}dumbass!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island is a famous\Nplace in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful Mermaids draw arcs\Nover the water and play with fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dream kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I be allowed to dream?! I'm a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They do have young ones there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not easy to get to this paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned about it being on the seabed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll see once we go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at the front page.\NIt's a recent newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fourteen more ships have\Ndisappeared this month."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Devil's Triangle,\Nalso known as the Florian Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't reach paradise without\Npassing through that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In that sea, more than 100\Nships go missing every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And after they go missing, sometimes\Nthe ships will show up with no crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and increasingly, people are seeing\Nghost ships with a dead crew on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghosts?! That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can meet skeletons that are alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of imagination do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I definitely don't wanna encounter them!\NI don't wanna even see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Such creepy ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens in that sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who encounter trouble\Nnever come back, so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dark sea with deep fog. So be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's a dangerous sea\Nwhere lots of disasters happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you are well\Nprepared before you set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with the stories about ghost ships--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words, wrecked trading\Nships and pirate ships--there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...legends of treasure ships, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find ghost ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If the worry's just about getting lost,\Ndon't worry, as we'll have plenty of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure ships, huh? I wonder\Nif they have swords, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What brought you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Franky asked us to bring you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The dream ship has been completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They built an incredible ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! It's already done?!\NThat was really quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Five top-notch shipwrights\Nworked on it day and night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's head there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you guys running that\Nfrantically for? You're out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, we came\Nto ask you a huge favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the wanted posters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanted posters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat, the bounty on\Nyour head has gotten crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the others, too, are wanted in addition!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too?! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of having me explain,\Njust take a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All seven of you now have\Nbounties on your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy, 300-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! It went up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Hunter Zoro, 120-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat Burglar Nami, 16 million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cotton Candy Lover Chopper,\Nthe gang's pet, 50-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil's Child Nico Robin,\N80-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Leg Sanji, failed to obtain\Na picture, 77-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sogeking's got a bounty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, we sympathize with you, or well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you wanna say all sorts\Nof things, but, well... please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The favor we're talking about\Nhas something to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyborg Franky, 44-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Bro's got a bounty on his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We somehow\Nwere able to get off the hook,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but Bro had no such luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If he stays in Water Seven,\Nhis life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:23:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If he gets caught again, we're not\Nstrong enough to rescue him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But he probably will try to stay on this\Nisland because he's worried about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we got together and discussed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat, please! You can\Ndo it by force if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take Bro out to sea.\NHe's a pirate's son to start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's go get our new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! So is that it, Luffy?! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky! Where are you, Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"The King of Animals that Overlooks the Sea!\NThe Dream Ship Magnificently Completed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
